<s> LDI Corp. , Cleveland , said it will offer $ 50 million in commercial paper backed by lease-rental receivables . </s>
<s> The program matches funds raised from the sale of the commercial paper with small to medium-sized leases . </s>
<s> LDI termed the paper `` non-recourse financing , '' meaning that investors would be repaid from the lease receivables , rather than directly by LDI Corp . </s>
<s> LDI leases and sells data-processing , telecommunications and other high-tech equipment . </s>
